      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BETTER CALL (8) is a fast dog well performed over the sprint races. Last start placegetter over 457m at Q Lakeside in a Mix 5 (25.96) but sharper journey suits this time. Form here at this distance is sound including two wins. Likely to feature again. DESTINI KRYSTAL (1) is going better than form suggests, missing the frame last time at this track but was placed three back followed by a close up fourth. Well placed here and should do much better. ELECTRIC MAN (3) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 19.27 beating SCOUT BOBBER. One of the key runners again. STRIKES TWICE (2) is in form and worth thought again.",
